00:01:28.570 --> 00:01:30.760
And there's a bunch of them and
we'll actually try to figure

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:32.540
out how many of them there are.

00:01:32.540 --> 00:01:38.060
But what is the probability of
this particular combination?

00:01:38.060 --> 00:01:41.950
Well, I have an 80% chance of
making this first basket.

00:01:41.950 --> 00:01:43.210
