00:01:53.460 --> 00:01:54.790
times 0.2.

00:01:54.790 --> 00:02:03.170
So this sequels 0.8 to the
third power times 0.2 squared.

00:02:03.170 --> 00:02:05.480
What's the probability of
getting this exact combination?

00:02:05.480 --> 00:02:08.650
Well, it's 0.8
times-- then I miss.

00:02:08.650 --> 00:02:10.110
There's a 20% chance of that.

00:02:10.110 --> 00:02:17.820
So times 0.2 times 0.8
times 0.2 times 0.8.

00:02:17.820 --> 00:02:20.190
We could rearrange this because
