00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:36.836
third times 0.2 squared.

00:02:36.836 --> 00:02:39.790
 

00:02:39.790 --> 00:02:44.340
The probability of getting any
particular combination of 3

00:02:44.340 --> 00:02:48.470
baskets and 2 misses is going
to be 0.8 to third

00:02:48.470 --> 00:02:51.470
times 0.2 squared.

00:02:51.470 --> 00:02:52.750
Now what's the total
probability of

00:02:52.750 --> 00:02:53.340
getting 3 out of 5?

00:02:53.340 --> 00:02:55.720
Well, it's going to be the sum
of all of these combinations.

00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:58.380
You know, I could list them
