00:03:02.520 --> 00:03:05.470
to figure out how many
different ways, if we have 5

00:03:05.470 --> 00:03:08.950
baskets and we're picking-- or
we have 5 shots and we're

00:03:08.950 --> 00:03:11.530
picking 3 of them to be the
ones that are basket shots.

00:03:11.530 --> 00:03:12.180
So what do I mean?

00:03:12.180 --> 00:03:21.670
So let's say my 5 shots-- you
know, I've shot 1, 2, 3, 4, 5.

00:03:21.670 --> 00:03:23.810
Out of these five, I'm
going to choose 3.

00:03:23.810 --> 00:03:26.140
So once again, I'm putting my
hat on as the god of

00:03:26.140 --> 00:03:30.850
probability and I will choose 3
of these shots to be the ones

00:03:30.850 --> 00:03:35.400
that happen to be the
ones that get made.

00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:41.030
So essentially, out of
5 I am choosing 3.

00:03:41.030 --> 00:03:43.400
5 choose 3.

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:44.630
And what does that equal to?

00:03:44.630 --> 00:03:52.520
That's 5 factorial over 3
factorial times 5 minus 3

00:03:52.520 --> 00:03:55.850
factorial, so that's
2 factorial.

00:03:55.850 --> 00:04:04.980
And that equals 5 times 4 times
3 times 2 times 1 over 3 times

00:04:04.980 --> 00:04:07.650
2 times 1 times 2 times 1.

00:04:07.650 --> 00:04:08.725
We can ignore all the 1's.

00:04:08.725 --> 00:04:09.220
Let's see.

00:04:09.220 --> 00:04:10.500
We get 3 times 2 times 1.

00:04:10.500 --> 00:04:11.480
3 times 2 times 1.

00:04:11.480 --> 00:04:13.490
We can cancel that.

00:04:13.490 --> 00:04:16.720
This 1 we can ignore, and
then this 2 and then

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:17.960
this turns into 2.

00:04:17.960 --> 00:04:20.130
So there are 10
possible combinations.

00:04:20.130 --> 00:04:20.980
These are two of them.

00:04:20.980 --> 00:04:23.710
You know, basket, basket,
basket, miss, miss.

00:04:23.710 --> 00:04:25.660
Basket, miss, basket,
miss, basket.

